text: "Funhouse" is a song by pop singer, Pink. It is the fifth release from her 2008 album, entitled the same as the name of the song, Funhouse. It tells of Pink's split with a partner. It reached 20th position in the UK Singles Chart. There is also a techno remix of the song. ==References== Category:2009 songs Category:Pink (singer) songs
title: Funhouse
